author: The Critical Drinker
description: Its nostalgia time! Join me and Danquish as we recount some of the best movies we grew up with in the 80s and 90s, why they were so iconic, what they meant to us, what they did for the Hollywood landscape, and ask the question, "What the hell happened to cinema?"
title: Drinker's Happy Hour - The Movies That Defined Our Generation
